README
======

Hi! I'm Hongbo, one of the co-maintainers of the Xen Project Hypervisor at
NixOS.

This branch is what I used to deploy my own production hypervisors. It contains
a bunch of commits cherry-picked from PR branches that are waiting to be merged.

└─ base (currently `nixpkgs:nixos-unstable`)
   ├─ PR #373294 xen: 4.19.1 -> 4.20.0
   │  ├─ Commit 39ae21f
   │  └─ Commit 3da13e2
   ├─ PR #374753 grub: build PVH variant of Grub2 for Xen
   │  ├─ Commit 04db5dc
   │  └─ Commit 114e81d
   └─ PR #365890 xen: patch `libxl` to search for `qemu-system-i386` properly
      └─ Commit a752b4b

